  "data": {
    "guidelines": [
      {
        "id": "DdCZOOwc81",
        "type": "do",
        "content": {
          "type": "doc",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Heading",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Be as engaging as it can be.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Use imperative verbs and sentence style.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Message",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "When writing about benefits of completing the task, use the future sense to create a human-like tone, for example, ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "you'll",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "italic"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " or ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "they'll",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "italic"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": ".",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "If the task completion will enable functionalities for other people, be clear about who's doing what by using phrases like ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "they'll",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "italic"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": ". ",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Call to action",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Use strong verbs that correspond to the headings and encourage action. This ensures that the user can act confidently even if they skip reading the body of the message.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "DMEE2QVRfq",
        "type": "dont",
        "content": {
          "type": "doc",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Heading",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Don't sacrifice clarity. Content testing will tell you if a specific phrase isn't clear to the target audience.  ",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Don't use initial capitalization.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Message",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Don't repeat the header. Instead, add details that will help the user succeed. ",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Don't use the present sense when writing about benefits of completing the task. The future tense, for example, ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "They'll manage users...,",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "italic"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " is a better choice, because onboarding requires a conversational tone.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Call to action",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Don't say \"OK\" or \"Close.\" Design options to close or skip cards on the container. ",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
